WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.080
[Tom] Hello, my name is Tom.

00:03.080 --> 00:05.380
[Tom] I am 27 years old.

00:05.380 --> 00:07.180
[Tom] I am from the USA.

00:07.180 --> 00:08.960
[Tom] I live in a big city.

00:08.960 --> 00:10.160
[Tom] I work in an office.

00:11.040 --> 00:12.720
[Maria] Hi, Tom.

00:12.720 --> 00:15.640
[Maria] My name is Maria.

00:15.640 --> 00:17.760
[Maria] I am 24 years old.

00:17.760 --> 00:20.220
[Maria] I am from Spain.

00:20.220 --> 00:22.500
[Maria] I live in a flat with my sister.

00:22.500 --> 00:24.040
[Maria] I work in a shop.

00:25.120 --> 00:28.740
[Ali] Hello, my name is Ali.

00:28.740 --> 00:31.180
[Ali] I am 29 years old.

00:31.180 --> 00:32.700
[Ali] I am from Turkey.

00:32.700 --> 00:34.420
[Ali] I live in a small house.

00:34.420 --> 00:35.900
[Ali] I am a driver.

00:36.820 --> 00:39.000
[Tom] Maria, do you like your city?

00:39.900 --> 00:42.120
[Maria] Yes, I do.

00:42.120 --> 00:45.100
[Maria] My city is small, but nice.

00:45.100 --> 00:47.400
[Maria] There are parks and shops.

00:47.400 --> 00:48.940
[Maria] Tom, do you like your city?

00:49.860 --> 00:51.740
[Tom] Yes, I do.

00:51.740 --> 00:53.940
[Tom] My city is big and busy.

00:53.940 --> 00:55.580
[Tom] There are many cars and people.

00:56.460 --> 00:58.420
[Ali] My city is not big.

00:58.420 --> 00:59.780
[Ali] It is quiet.

00:59.780 --> 01:00.620
[Ali] I like it.

01:01.500 --> 01:04.780
[Maria] Ali, do you live with your family?

01:05.700 --> 01:07.560
[Ali] Yes, I do.

01:07.560 --> 01:09.780
[Ali] I live with my mother and father.

01:09.780 --> 01:10.860
[Ali] And you, Maria?

01:11.780 --> 01:13.540
[Maria] I live with my sister.

01:13.540 --> 01:15.680
[Maria] We like to talk and watch TV.

01:16.640 --> 01:18.140
[Tom] I live alone.

01:18.140 --> 01:20.300
[Tom] I do not have a big family.

01:21.180 --> 01:24.560
[Ali] Tom, what do you do every day?

01:24.560 --> 01:26.280
[Tom] I get up at eight o'clock.

01:26.280 --> 01:27.700
[Tom] I have breakfast.

01:27.700 --> 01:28.960
[Tom] I go to work.

01:28.960 --> 01:31.040
[Tom] I work on my computer.

01:31.040 --> 01:32.700
[Tom] I come home at six o'clock.

01:33.620 --> 01:35.700
[Maria] I get up at seven o'clock.

01:35.700 --> 01:37.600
[Maria] I go to work.

01:37.600 --> 01:39.820
[Maria] I help people in the shop.

01:39.820 --> 01:41.440
[Maria] I come home at five o'clock.

01:42.300 --> 01:44.240
[Ali] I get up at six o'clock.

01:44.240 --> 01:46.380
[Ali] I drive a car all day.

01:46.380 --> 01:48.220
[Ali] I come home and have dinner.

01:49.140 --> 01:51.020
[Tom] What do you do in the evening?

01:51.940 --> 01:54.940
[Maria] In the evening, I cook and talk with my sister.

01:54.940 --> 01:56.600
[Maria] I sometimes watch TV.

01:57.480 --> 02:00.120
[Ali] I watch TV or rest.

02:00.120 --> 02:01.560
[Ali] I am very tired.

02:02.440 --> 02:04.860
[Tom] I read books or watch films.

02:05.720 --> 02:08.120
[Maria] Tom, do you like your job?

02:08.960 --> 02:11.020
[Tom] Yes, I do.

02:11.020 --> 02:12.540
[Tom] I like my job.

02:12.540 --> 02:14.120
[Tom] It is interesting.

02:14.120 --> 02:15.040
[Tom] And you?

02:15.940 --> 02:18.680
[Maria] Yes, I like my job too.

02:18.680 --> 02:19.960
[Maria] I like people.

02:20.840 --> 02:23.540
[Ali] I like my job, but it is hard.

02:24.420 --> 02:27.180
[Tom] What do you like to do in your free time?

02:27.180 --> 02:29.660
[Maria] I like music and films.

02:29.660 --> 02:31.340
[Maria] I also like walking.

02:32.260 --> 02:34.580
[Ali] I like walking and talking with friends.

02:35.460 --> 02:37.460
[Tom] I like sports and books.

02:37.460 --> 02:38.420
[Tom] I play football.

02:39.300 --> 02:41.040
[Maria] What food do you like?

02:41.940 --> 02:44.380
[Ali] I like rice and meat.

02:44.380 --> 02:46.980
[Ali] I also like soup.

02:46.980 --> 02:48.100
[Ali] I drink water.

02:49.020 --> 02:51.100
[Tom] I like pasta and chicken.

02:51.100 --> 02:52.220
[Tom] I drink coffee.

02:53.100 --> 02:58.100
[Maria] I like salad, bread, and fruit.

02:58.100 --> 02:59.700
[Maria] I drink tea.

03:00.580 --> 03:02.780
[Ali] Do you like coffee, Maria?

03:02.780 --> 03:05.220
[Maria] No, I do not.

03:05.220 --> 03:06.340
[Maria] I like tea.

03:07.260 --> 03:08.760
[Tom] I like coffee very much.

03:09.660 --> 03:10.960
[Maria] Nice to meet you.

03:11.860 --> 03:13.120
[Ali] Nice to meet you.

03:14.020 --> 03:15.180
[Tom] Nice to meet you.
